title: 13 killed after falling into well at marriage function in UP's Kushinagar - Times of India

description: Thirteen women and children, all girls, died after falling into a well while performing a marriage ritual in Uttar Pradesh's Kushinagar district, police said on Thursday. The incident, in which at least 10 people were also injured, took place at Naurangiya Tola village when an iron grille, they were sitting on, broke, they said. Chief Minister Yogi Adityanath and Prime Minister Narendra Modi have expressed grief over the incident.
